  "title": "Full Time Landscape Worker (On Job Training)",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li><strong>Salary :$1950</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Working days &amp; hours: 8am – 5pm (Monday – Friday), 8am – 12am (Saturday)</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Location: Various location in Singapore</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Well Established Landscape Company</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Job Scope</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Watering of plants and removal of weeds or unwanted plants.</li>\n  <li>Pruning of low shrubs.</li>\n  <li>Forking soil.</li>\n  <li>Clearing dry leaves</li>\n  <li>Propagation of plants.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirement</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>No experience required; Training provided.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Candidates are encouraged to apply this position via Apply Now button with the following information in the resume:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Work experiences and job responsibilities</li>\n  <li>Current and Expected salary</li>\n  <li>Reason for leaving</li>\n  <li>Date of availability</li>\n  <li>Education background</li>\n</ul>\n<p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be contacted.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>YEOW CHANG FU (R23118759)</p>\n<p>EA Recruitment Pte Ltd</p>\n<p>EA License No: 21C0492</p>",
